{
  "stem": "3721.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they came home visiting and claiming how many Jews they murdered.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And quite bragging about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Of course, nobody believed it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I did believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Of course, then we approaching of 1944, I'm sure you know that the Hungarian Jews were molested, but not too much.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Until 1944, I believe, March the 15th or March something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say very uncomfortable.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because, at that time until the end of 1943-- actually June of 1943, I was going to school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my classmates who were non-Jews, except-- exception of one or two, were very, very antisemitic. and continuously telling me, what are you studying for?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As I mentioned before.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're going to kill you anyway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why do you have to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] have to bother even?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, well, I still like to have a profession because somehow, I will-- I will-- hoping to survive.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I'm building my own future.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And then in 1943 in June, I finished school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as I told you before, I could not get a job in the defense industry.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because everything was defense.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I worked with my father and I learned to be a dental technician.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Until, 19-- I believe, March 1944, the government of Hungary was overthrown and a new government was appointed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Quisling-- I don't remember his name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were overran by German SS troopers and Hungarian gendarmes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I remember, it was very frightening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because the Jews were forbidden to go the streets after dark.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were obliged to wear a yellow armband with a Magen David.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And our movements were totally restricted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were not allowed to go to school anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Although, that didn't somehow involve me, personally, but my brothers and my sisters, it did.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
